古巴的部落客們持續不斷地更新[近期受打壓的](https://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/07/18/cuba-female-
activists-reportedly-beatendetained/
"https://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/07/18/cuba-female-activists-reportedly-
beatendetained/")白色婦女運動（[Las Damas de
Blanco](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ladies_in_White
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ladies_in_White")）相關文章，並指出部份參加運動的成員“[在離開教堂時被卡斯特羅國家安全局（Castro
State Security）的人員攻擊與毒打](http://babalublog.com/2011/07/ladies-in-white-
violently-attacked-yesterday-by-castro-state-security/
"http://babalublog.com/2011/07/ladies-in-white-violently-attacked-yesterday-
by-castro-state-security/")”。

[美國古巴裔婦女聯盟](http://coalitionofcubanamericanwomen.blogspot.com/2011/07/ladies-
in-white-beaten-dragged-and.html
"http://coalitionofcubanamericanwomen.blogspot.com/2011/07/ladies-in-white-
beaten-dragged-and.html")發布新聞稿指責該次攻擊事件，新聞稿包含了一段該事件當事人Tania Montoya
Vázquez講述該次經驗的[錄音片段](http://www.martinoticias.com/noticias/Agreden-a-
opositoras-en-Santiago-de-Cuba--125710308.html
"http://www.martinoticias.com/noticias/Agreden-a-opositoras-en-Santiago-de-
Cuba--125710308.html")[西語]。El Cafe
Cubano部落格[重新發布了該聯盟的新聞稿](http://elcubanocafe.blogspot.com/2011/07/cuba-ladies-
in-white-beaten-dragged.html "http://elcubanocafe.blogspot.com/2011/07/cuba-
ladies-in-white-beaten-dragged.html")。

